fr.uga.pddl4j.parser

Enum Connective

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Connective>
      • fr.uga.pddl4j.parser.Connective
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Connective>

    public enum Connective
extends java.lang.Enum<Connective>
    This enumeration defines the connective that can be used in PDDL expressions implemented by the class Exp.
